<li>Why need regulation ?
<ul>
<li>India- 2nd highest no. of internet and mobile subscribers- unregulated
<ul>
<li><strong>Print media- regulated by Press Council of India</strong></li>
<li>TV (Both News+Entertainment)= Cable Networks Regulation Act 2005</li>
<li>Online content= lacks regulation</li></ul></li>
<li>Controversies
<ul>
<li>Gunjan Saxena- IAF commented;</li>
