<li><u>Cons</u>-
<ul>
<li>No details mentioned by govt/ what is the plan ?</li>
<li>Restricting contents contradicting govt</li>
<li>Regional cinema got exposure due to OTT</li>
<li>USA, Canada, Aus, South Africa, EU- Developed- DONT regulate internet content
<ul>
<li>China, Russia, Islamic nations- not free</li>
<li>India- mixed bag (partly regulated/free)</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>
